caption: I love December and I LOVE Christmas music, so every day this month I am going to make a shuttersong with Christmas music! I'd love to welcome you all to join in! I will be using the hashtag #HappyHolidaysShuttersong to share the posts. ☃⛄️ (PS: If you don't celebrate Christmas, feel free to add your own holiday's music! That is why I chose the hashtag happy holidays and not Merry Christmas. I personally will post Christmas music because it's what I celebrate.)
song_album: Christmas Coming Home (feat. Lennon & Maisy) - Single
